name: nSocket
description: nSocket is a high performance Lightweight Network Framework which is based on JAVA NIO.1 and java NIO.2. Building this project is for easier coding network programs,the difference between nSocket and Mina or Netty is that nSocket will use NIO.2 to build asynchronous communication, further more, on the final edition of nSocket, the pattern of architecture will be based on P2P module.
